        <h3>Ethical Behavior and Decision-Making</h3>
        <p>Leaders should model ethical behavior and decision-making. Upholding ethical standards fosters trust and integrity within the organization. Leaders must consider the ethical implications of their decisions on individuals and the broader organization.</p>
    </div>

